title: Alibates Flint Quarries National Monument: Photo Gallery
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Photo Gallery              Photo Gallery                    Take a virtual hike to the Alibates Flint Quarries!   10 Photos  View photos and learn a bit about the resources that enabled cultures to thrive on the southern Great Plains for generations.          Landscape Photos   13 Photos  Landscapes of Alibates Flint Quarries National Monument.          2015 Events at Alibates   4 Photos  2015 was the 50th anniversary of the Alibates Flint Quarries National Monument and we hosted a series of fun events.
